def file_to_image(file):
    unique = str(uuid.uuid4())[:8]
    extension = os.path.splitext(file.filename)[1]
    file_path   = f"tmp/{unique}{extension}"
    with open(file_path, "wb") as buffer:
        shutil.copyfileobj(file.file, buffer)
    return file_path
